      <text bytes="5152" xml:space="preserve">{{Distinguish|text = [[Collision (telecommunications)|Packet collision]] in telecommunications}}
{{Multiple issues|
{{One source|date=May 2013}}
{{More citations needed |date=May 2013}}
{{Self-published|date=May 2013}}
