*[[Hash table#Collision resolution|Collision resolution]] (hash tables)
*[[Cryptographic hash function]]
*[[Name collision]], accidental use of identical variable names
*[[Password hash]] (key derivation function)
*[[Perfect hash function]], a hash function that is free of collisions by design
*[[Preimage attack]]
*[[Provably secure hash function]]
*[[Random oracle]]

